      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software version control, documented test suite, and traceable build process must be demonstrated at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is a commercially validated code with documented QA procedures. Version control logs and regression test results were reviewed and confirmed consistent with Gradation 2 requirements for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
