      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2 Gradation 1, equivalency of input parameters between validation and COU contexts must be qualitatively addressed.",
      "rationale": "Input parameters in the validation model were confirmed to be equivalent to the COU simulation inputs. Fluid properties, boundary condition types, and turbulence model settings were held constant between the validation and COU prediction runs, ensuring direct transferability of the validation evidence."
    }
